ike":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T17:29:37.000Z","msg":"佢應該唔係想同你討論膠樽入熱水會唔會有毒氣<br />\n<br />\n佢想借呢件事話比你知condom都會有滲漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"磨擦到100度高溫？定啲精熱到溶到膠？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T18:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb48c698738fb38fc4291494198d8f8eb49117c2","tid":2305530,"uid":14503,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"eefc6a3afd54ffa02a592f3971a2386ceef6f01d","tid":2305530,"uid":42595,"like":2,"dislike":30,"score":-28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T17:08:43.000Z","msg":"全部討論係基於普通道地綠茶膠樽<br />\n依家個問題係如果入邊啲水有毒<br />\n咁正正常常如果你唔係飲嗰啲水都唔會中毒<br />\n<br />\n因為佢就同我講就算閂埋蓋呢啲有毒氣體都可能會洩漏出嚟<br />\n<br />\n我覺得非常之戇鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T18:32:36.000Z","msg":"咁睇吓有幾毒囉，加熱個陣直頭有臭味啦嗰啲咪毒，毒唔死你咁解姐。就咁靜態放啲毒水喺入面唔係話唔會洩漏但洩漏出嚟嗰啲有毒物質一樣係毒你唔死咁解姐"},{"pid":"b234446807769a716438d91174b719c735b21fc7","tid":2305530,"uid":368978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T18:34:37.000Z","msg":"密封咗就唔會出到黎"},{"pid":"3bf64126a19eb63c9e1cc274251e26478dcfc357","tid":2305530,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T18:36:18.000Z","msg":"你到滾水入去嗰陣時咪會聞到臭味囉嗰啲臭味咪有毒囉，同埋入面熱都會傳到出面熱，即係出面都會溶膠，咁出面個表面就有毒，熱到氣化咗咪就係你聞到嘅毒氣囉。咁你還有毒定無毒？"},{"pid":"7861791d0bb3d66340edc6ce37ce02898555abbd","tid":2305530,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T18:41:40.000Z","msg":"點先算有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0faaac290467437335403512155587ce223e5c1f","tid